name: Kay Jewelers Retail Locations, USA, 12.2008
description: This dataset locates all the Kay Jewelers across the USA as of 12.2008. The data comes from kay Jewelers website at kay.com and includes: shopping center, address, city, state, zip, phone and lat/lon location. The lat/lon location were determined through the use of a geocoder found at batchgeocode.com
